<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>About Us - The Daily Dairy</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .about-hero {
      background: url('/images/about-hero.png') center center/cover no-repeat;
      height: 300px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      position: relative;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2.75rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    }
    .about-list li {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<div class="container py-5" style="max-width:900px;">
  <div class="about-hero">About The Daily Dairy</div>

  <p class="lead mb-4">
    Welcome to <strong>The Daily Dairy</strong> — your trusted platform to share stories, ideas, and connect with a vibrant writing community.
  </p>

  <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <img src="/images/team-collaboration.png" alt="Team Collaboration" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Our Mission</h3>
      <p>
        Founded in <%= new Date().getFullYear() %>, we empower creators to tell their stories, build audiences, and engage meaningfully. Our platform fuels creativity, respect, and community connection.
      </p>
      <ul class="about-list list-unstyled ps-3">
        <li>📝 Easy publishing & editing tools</li>
        <li>👀 Discover trending content daily</li>
        <li>❤️ Engage through likes, bookmarks, and comments</li>
        <li>🔒 Respect for your privacy and data security</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="fs-5">
    We’re always improving — send your feedback or inquiries via our <a href="/contact" class="link-primary">Contact page</a>.
  </p>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
